{"tid":680231,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"西環台灣食店「請坐」關注組，提防尖咀冒牌貨","createTime":"2018-05-27T05:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T12:37:49.000Z","uid":89349,"like":72,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"cb22b3d4dda7e716d69725629597750375c1b981","tid":680231,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/131406_cccfa9528bf8b056cdc9b36079acfec5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F131406_cccfa9528bf8b056cdc9b36079acfec5.png&h=b0c5225b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n衣間野d牛肉麵同蛋餅好好食，希望正店快d開番啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家千祈唔好去幫趁間冒牌貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be16141272b44f3ca2c16f09812c2b9bb163ebf","tid":680231,"uid":43575,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:40:03.000Z","msg":"牛肉麵有咩好食？"},{"pid":"2694f3fd0f22a29d88a9c8f8061d004a3b4f0fce","tid":680231,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:47:15.000Z","msg":"點呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375dd538501fe5565e09ffa028b8407b72166d57","tid":680231,"uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0be16141272b44f3ca2c16f09812c2b9bb163ebf","tid":680231,"uid":43575,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:40:03.000Z","msg":"牛肉麵有咩好食？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:48:13.000Z","msg":"個湯底煮得好食，麵質又彈牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb14ff9799d685f4467237966c67c4ca020c9c7","tid":680231,"uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2694f3fd0f22a29d88a9c8f8061d004a3b4f0fce","tid":680231,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:47:15.000Z","msg":"點呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lom